room_title: Escape room "The Principal's Office" by North Valley Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 42302 N Vision Way, Suite 104, Anthem, AZ 85086
room_description: Joe Curtis, the star quarterback, needs your help! He is failing a class. Oh no! If his mom finds out, he won't be able to play in the big game this Friday. You need to help him switch his failing report card with a good report card so he can lead the team to victory. Go Warthogs!
